  "title": "Activated Carbon vs Baking Soda: The Ultimate Comparison",
  "excerpt": "Baking soda failing? See why 89% switch to activated carbon. Shocking test reveals which works better for cat litter smell!",
  "content": "<header class=\"mb-12\">\n            <h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">\n              Activated Carbon vs Baking Soda: The Ultimate Comparison\n            </h1>\n            <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed\">\n              Two popular odor control technologies go head-to-head. We examine the science, effectiveness, and real-world performance of each approach.\n            </p>\n          </header>\n\n          <div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-dark\">\n            <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">\n              When it comes to controlling cat litter odors, two main technologies dominate the market: activated carbon and baking soda.\n              Both have their merits, but which one actually delivers better results for cat owners?\n            </p>\n\n            <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">\n              How Each Technology Works\n            </h2>\n\n            <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 my-8\">\n              <div class=\"bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 p-6 rounded-lg\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200\">\n                  Activated Carbon\n                </h3>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">\n                  Works through <strong>molecular adsorption</strong>. The porous structure traps odor molecules\n                  inside microscopic pores, physically removing them from the air.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n\n              <div class=\"bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-900/20 p-6 rounded-lg\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-orange-800 dark:text-orange-200\">\n                  Baking Soda\n                </h3>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">\n                  Works through <strong>pH neutralization</strong>. Alkaline properties neutralize acidic odor\n                  compounds, reducing their smell intensity.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"mb-8\">\n              \n              <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center mt-2\">\n                Performance testing reveals significant differences between technologies\n              </p>\n            </div>\n\n            <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">\n              Performance Comparison\n            </h2>\n\n            <div class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n              <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 my-8\">\n                <thead>\n                  <tr class=\"bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800\">\n                    <th class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-left text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">Factor</th>\n                    <th class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-left text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200\">Activated Carbon</th>\n                    <th class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-left text-orange-800 dark:text-orange-200\">Baking Soda</th>\n                  </tr>\n                </thead>\n                <tbody>\n                  <tr>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">Odor Elimination</td>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">Physically removes odor molecules</td>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">Neutralizes some odor compounds</td>\n                  </tr>\n                  <tr>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">Duration</td>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">4-6 weeks effectiveness</td>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">1-2 weeks effectiveness</td>\n                  </tr>\n                  <tr>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">Coverage</td>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">Wide spectrum of odors</td>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">Limited to acidic odors</td>\n                  </tr>\n                  <tr>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">Natural</td>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">100% natural carbon</td>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">Natural mineral compound</td>\n                  </tr>\n                </tbody>\n              </table>\n            </div>\n\n            <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">\n              The Verdict\n            </h2>\n\n            <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">\n              While both technologies have their place, activated carbon offers superior performance for cat litter odor control.\n              Its ability to physically trap a wide range of odor molecules, combined with longer-lasting effectiveness,\n              makes it the preferred choice for serious odor elimination.\n            </p>\n\n            <div class=\"bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 border-l-4 border-green-500 dark:border-green-700 p-6 my-8\">\n              <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-green-800 dark:text-green-200 mb-2\">\n                Pro Tip for Cat Owners\n              </h3>\n              <p class=\"text-green-700 dark:text-green-300\">\n                For maximum effectiveness, choose activated carbon products made from coconut shells,\n                as they offer the highest porosity and adsorption capacity.\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <footer class=\"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700\">\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400\">\n              Published on January 15, 2024 |\n              <a href=\"/blog\">\n                Back to Blog\n              </a>\n            </p>\n          </footer>",
